title: Genetic variants may influence poststroke recovery

title_detail.value: Genetic variants may influence poststroke recovery

summary: Our genes may have a bearing not only on our stroke risk, but probably also on how well we recover after stroke. For the first time, scientists have identified common genetic variants that are associated with outcome after ischemic stroke.
